comments: Paul (PHX) extends his forearm slightly into Conley (UTA) during the drive, and the contact is marginal.
Whiteside (UTA) initiates and delivers contact as he goes through Smith's (PHX) space and dislodges him on the screen.
All Technical Fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
O'Neale (UTA) engages with Booker (PHX) off-ball and separates.
O'Neale (UTA) is retracting his hand when he makes marginal contact with Booker's (PHX) arm as he gathers the ball.
Biyombo (PHX) and Paschall (UTA) both engage and separate during the rebound.
Paschall (UTA) makes incidental leg-to-leg contact with Johnson (PHX) as he secures the rebound and passes.
Clarkson (UTA) commits a take foul on Biyombo (PHX) away from the ball.
Bogdanovic (UTA) extends his arms into Biyombo's (PHX) back as Biyombo attempts to screen.
Bridges (PHX) legally contests Clarkson's (UTA) jump shot attempt.
O'Neale (UTA) fouls Bridges (PHX) on the perimeter.
O'Neale (UTA) and Johnson (PHX) make incidental contact as they both move toward the perimeter.
Smith (PHX) and O'Neale (UTA) engage and separate during the loose ball.
PHX commits a 24-second shot clock violation.
